        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-8" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;fontSize=13;" value="The Business&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;Digger&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="120" x="1500" y="617.25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-10" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;The Business Digger&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;O que ele faz:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ingestão de manuais de processos, glossários, transcrições de reuniões com stakeholders e regras normativas (ex: protocolos de gestão, cálculos ideais de DPO -&amp;nbsp;&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;175&quot;&gt;Days Payable Outstanding&lt;/i&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;O que ele gera:&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;O&amp;nbsp;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;18&quot;&gt;Grafo Conceitual (&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;36&quot;&gt;To-Be&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;Intencional)&lt;/b&gt;. Ele diz: &quot;A &#39;Gestão de Risco do Fornecedor&#39; é um conceito totalmente separado do &#39;Pagamento de Faturas&#39;&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="212.75" width="380" x="1500" y="777.25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-12" parent="1" style="shape=image;html=1;verticalAlign=top;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=#ffffff;imageAspect=0;aspect=fixed;image=https://icons.diagrams.net/icon-cache1/Logos_Microsoft_Office_365-2232/Microsoft_Office-07-1169.svg" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="78" width="78" x="1340" y="492" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-14" parent="1" style="sketch=0;points=[[0,0,0],[0.25,0,0],[0.5,0,0],[0.75,0,0],[1,0,0],[0,1,0],[0.25,1,0],[0.5,1,0],[0.75,1,0],[1,1,0],[0,0.25,0],[0,0.5,0],[0,0.75,0],[1,0.25,0],[1,0.5,0],[1,0.75,0]];outlineConnect=0;fontColor=#232F3E;fillColor=#C925D1;strokeColor=#ffffff;dashed=0;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;align=center;html=1;fontSize=12;fontStyle=0;aspect=fixed;shape=mxgraph.aws4.resourceIcon;resIcon=mxgraph.aws4.aurora;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="78" width="78" x="426" y="488.5" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-23" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontSize=16;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;DDD Solution Space&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="284" x="216" y="330" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="-ppM35XShmB3G3ZkOoFj-24" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontSize=16;align=right;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;DDD Problem Space&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="284" x="1416" y="330" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="BTIGgISosB7TfDn9JsR0-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;1. Artefatos do Espaço do Problema (Descoberta e Requisitos)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Nesta etapa (frequentemente chamada de Design Estratégico), o foco é entender &quot;o que&quot; o negócio faz, descobrindo processos, atores e a linguagem do domínio.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Glossário Visual (&lt;em&gt;Visual Glossary&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;: É o artefato físico ou digital onde a Linguagem Ubíqua é formalmente documentada, garantindo que o vocabulário do domínio tenha um único significado para todos os envolvidos.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Domain Stories (Histórias de Domínio)&lt;/strong&gt;: Diagramas criados no&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Domain Storytelling&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;que revelam como o negócio atua na prática, mostrando quem são os atores, quais atividades executam e com quais objetos de trabalho eles interagem.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quadros de&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;EventStorming&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;em&gt;Big Picture&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;e Nível de Processo)&lt;/strong&gt;: Painéis repletos de notas adesivas (&lt;em&gt;post-its&lt;/em&gt;) que mapeiam fluxos e linhas do tempo do negócio, identificando os&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Eventos de Domínio&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(coisas importantes que já aconteceram),&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Comandos&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(ações) e&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Políticas&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(regras de negócio).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mapas de Subdomínios (&lt;em&gt;Domain Charts&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;: Documentos que categorizam as áreas do negócio em Subdomínios&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Core&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(o diferencial competitivo),&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Supporting&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(apoio) e&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Generic&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(genérico), ajudando a definir onde alocar mais recursos de desenvolvimento.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mapas de Jornadas (&lt;em&gt;Event Modeling&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;: O mapeamento das jornadas de usuário e integrações de API que detalham como o cliente atinge seus objetivos.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Artefatos de Ideação&lt;/strong&gt;: O começo do projeto pode gerar um&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Business Model Canvas&lt;/em&gt;, mapas de impacto (&lt;em&gt;Impact Mapping&lt;/em&gt;) e mapas de capacidades (&lt;em&gt;Wardley Maps&lt;/em&gt;) para alinhar a visão de negócio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="680" width="1160" x="2000" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="BTIGgISosB7TfDn9JsR0-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h3 style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;2. Artefatos do Espaço da Solução (Design Arquitetural e Tático)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Nesta fase, as informações do espaço do problema são transformadas em estruturas de software e limites de contexto.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design Estratégico da Solução (Alto Nível)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bounded Context Canvas&lt;/strong&gt;: Um template prático e visual que documenta o escopo de um&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Bounded Context&lt;/em&gt;(Contexto Delimitado). Ele especifica a finalidade daquele contexto, sua classificação estratégica, as regras de negócios principais e as mensagens de entrada e saída (Comandos, Queries e Eventos).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mapas de Contexto (&lt;em&gt;Context Maps&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;: Diagramas arquiteturais que definem os padrões de integração e o relacionamento (como&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Partnership&lt;/em&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Shared Kernel&lt;/em&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Anticorruption Layer&lt;/em&gt;) entre os diversos Contextos Delimitados e sistemas externos ou legados.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contratos de API e Esquemas de Eventos&lt;/strong&gt;: Definições claras sobre a comunicação entre serviços baseadas nos artefatos desenvolvidos previamente.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design Tático (Baixo Nível e Código)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;O Modelo de Domínio (&lt;em&gt;Domain Model&lt;/em&gt;)&lt;/strong&gt;: A implementação em código que espelha os processos de negócio. Ele é estruturado através dos padrões táticos do DDD, como os&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Agregados&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;em&gt;Aggregates&lt;/em&gt;),&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Entidades&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;em&gt;Entities&lt;/em&gt;), e&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Objetos de Valor&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;(&lt;em&gt;Value Objects&lt;/em&gt;).&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Critérios de Aceite e Especificações Executáveis&lt;/strong&gt;: Testes formulados a partir de sessões de&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Example Mapping&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;ou escritos com sintaxes BDD (Behavior-Driven Development), focados em validar regras de negócios e políticas antes do desenvolvimento em si.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;API Product Canvas&lt;/strong&gt;: Usado para projetar APIs REST e eventos alinhados ao domínio.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Architecture Communication Canvas&lt;/strong&gt;: Um artefato auxiliar que documenta decisões sobre os serviços, repositórios e a arquitetura tática implantada.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="840" width="1160" x="-1240" y="240" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qf6w_oclYkT93tvNgyl2-1" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="763" width="1200" x="-2530" y="-1680" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qf6w_oclYkT93tvNgyl2-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h3 style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;br class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;Remodelagem de Domínios a partir da LLM&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h1 style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid; margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;A funçāo do especialista de domínio nāo corrompido é de a cada nova iteraçāo de desenvolvimento, ir remodelando os subdomínios para os seus respectivos lugares, ou até mais, dado o conjunto de insumos a ser considerado, podendo até remodelar os subdomínios principais.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="250" width="760" x="-1250" y="-1680" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="qf6w_oclYkT93tvNgyl2-4" parent="1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="1222" width="2304" x="-200" y="1400" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hFOdBsxGvuDd8xlWKRMj-2" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;fontSize=16;align=center;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Reconciliação Semântica&lt;/h1&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="284" x="820" y="-590" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hFOdBsxGvuDd8xlWKRMj-3" parent="1" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;fontSize=13;" value="The Lexicon Weaver" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="120" width="120" x="902" y="-470" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="hFOdBsxGvuDd8xlWKRMj-4" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;align=left;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;The Lexicon Weaver&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;markdown markdown-main-panel stronger enable-updated-hr-color&quot; id=&quot;model-response-message-contentr_9f68c6409ff85b9a&quot; aria-live=&quot;polite&quot; aria-busy=&quot;false&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid; font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;O&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;the-lexicon-weaver&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(O Tecelão do Léxico) é o árbitro semântico e a &quot;Pedra de Roseta&quot; do nosso ecossistema de agentes voltado para o Domain-Driven Design. Posicionado estrategicamente no centro da arquitetura, a sua missão exclusiva é resolver conflitos de comunicação e forjar a&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;281&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Linguagem Ubíqua Oficial&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;do sistema.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Aqui estão as suas características principais:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul data-path-to-node=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;padding-inline-start: 32px; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Ponto de Convergência:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Ele não lê código-fonte nem entrevista humanos. Ele atua consumindo e cruzando os relatórios gerados pelo&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;129&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;the-code-digger&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(que mapeou a realidade física e corrompida do legado) e pelo&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;2,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;207&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;the-business-digger&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(que mapeou a intenção pura e estratégica do negócio).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Auditoria Linguística Implacável:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;O agente é programado para caçar&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;67&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;falsos cognatos&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(quando o código e o negócio usam a mesma palavra para significados diferentes), colapsar&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;173&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;sinônimos descontrolados&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;do banco de dados e revelar&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;2,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;226&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;conceitos implícitos&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;que operam nas sombras de lógicas antigas (os famosos &quot;ifs&quot; obscuros).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Filtro de Toxicidade:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Ele atua como uma barreira sanitária. O agente identifica e rotula o jargão viciado e as limitações físicas do sistema antigo (ex:&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;153&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Tb_Geral&lt;/code&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;163&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Calc_1&lt;/code&gt;) como&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;2,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;176&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Léxico Tóxico&lt;/b&gt;, garantindo que esses termos sejam banidos da nova modelagem.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;O Entregável:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Um Dicionário de Linguagem Ubíqua limpo, definitivo e incontestável, que servirá como o contrato fundacional para o próximo passo do&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;147&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;the-context-mapper&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;(na criação de&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;i data-path-to-node=&quot;3&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;181&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Bounded Contexts&lt;/i&gt;) e para as equipas de engenharia que forem construir os novos microsserviços.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="270" width="640" x="-200" y="-560" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
